splashtext[3]="I'm always squeezing the trigger! Should I not be do that-? …doing that?"
splashtext[4]="It's all- this is all mechanically necessary!"
splashtext[5]="They don't- There's no article about that on Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia!"
splashtext[6]="I drink soda for lunch!"
splashtext[7]="Mr. Kid! Be careful! More careful... #than a badger going after a... a den of snakes!"
splashtext[8]="Black Mesa makes ALL the Powerade™!"
splashtext[9]="This is all instinct, Mr. Kid! I'm scared!"
splashtext[10]="I can recognize Beyblades when I see 'em!"
