splashtext[12]="This is all built to CODE!! It'll be okay."
splashtext[13]="Grab a soda, Mr. Kid! It'll help you see faster!"
splashtext[14]="When we get outta here I'm gonna write #the Wikipedia article for the the uh the Black Mesa Golem Ape!"
splashtext[15]="OH MY GOD WE'RE DOOOMMMEDD"
